Package: librust-libconfig-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libconfig-dev
Description: Safe Rust bindings for libconfig C library
 Provides a safe Rust wrapper around the libconfig C configuration
 library with full type safety, lifetime management, and all
 libconfig 1.1.x through 1.8.x features.